      • exportAll

        public void exportAll(java.util.ArrayList<Room> rlist)
               throws java.io.FileNotFoundException
        This method exports every Room object stored in the rlist to RoomList.txt. It calls the export function repeatedly until it reaches the end of rlist.
        Parameters:
        rlist - This ArrayList contains all the new updates made from the user and the existing ones.
        Throws:
        java.io.FileNotFoundException
